  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in the tagine over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chicken and cook until browned on all sides, about 5-7 minutes.",
    "Add the carrots, potatoes, cumin, coriander, turmeric, salt, and black pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Pour in the chicken broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Cover the tagine and transfer to the oven. Cook at 300°F for 30 minutes.",
    "Remove the tagine from the oven and stir in the lime juice.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh parsley, if desired."
